text.tspan: Grab Proto Zell and drop into Dish.
The Zell will be transmitted as a Signal.
Point the Receiver Scope at the Zell.
Drop the Text Zell into the Dish.
The Receiver Scope shows the received Signal.
Point the Text Scope at the
Text Zell and change its value.
Pick the Text Zell up and drop it again.
The Receiver Scope shows the new received Signal.
